[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1395","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1395.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1205","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9127,\"outputTokens\":18,\"totalTokens\":10809}}","description":"HP-UX 10.00 和 10.01 版本中的 nettune 工具以 setuid root 权限安装，导致本地用户可通过修改关键网络配置信息触发拒绝服务漏洞。该漏洞源于 nettune 程序以 root 权限运行且缺乏适当的权限检查，本地攻击者可利用该工具修改关键网络配置参数，导致网络服务中断或系统网络功能瘫痪。攻击条件要求攻击者拥有本地系统访问权限，利用方式为直接调用 nettune 工具修改网络配置参数。CVSS 评分 2.1，属于低危本地拒绝服务漏洞，影响范围限于 HP-UX 10.00 和 10.01 版本。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1205"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1996-06-07T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:56.627","remediation":"升级到 HP-UX 10.20 或更高版本以修复该缺陷；在无法立即升级时，使用 chmod u-s /usr/sbin/nettune 移除 nettune 的 setuid root 权限，并限制仅 root 可访问，防止本地用户篡改关键网络配置引发拒绝服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602167419195&w=2","http://packetstormsecurity.org/advisories/ibm-ers/96-08","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/414","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/1999/CVE-1999-1205.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2126251525a2d370ea93bd7affc3a9b71b419b4c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1205.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1205","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d281505551869bb381f43b6d1c6cb3abf45ad885/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1205.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1205.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1205.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87927/info.html","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--3a9247bd-e6da-452a-8f08-55dbae981900.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1205.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1395.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1428","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1428.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1253","title":"SCO OpenServer和SCO Internet FastStart 内核错误处理权限提升漏洞","description":"SCO OpenServer 5.0.2及更早版本与SCO Internet FastStart 1.0的内核错误处理例程中存在权限许可和访问控制漏洞。本地用户可通过向系统发送特制请求触发内核错误处理缺陷，绕过安全检查并获取root权限。该漏洞影响范围广，攻击条件为拥有本地访问权限，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1253"],"sources":["cve","avd"],"published":"1996-06-07","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"安装SCO安全公告SB.96:01a提供的内核补丁修复错误处理例程中的权限缺陷。对于无法安装补丁的系统，限制非信任用户的本地登录访问并通过最小权限原则严格控制用户对内核接口的调用权限。由于SCO OpenServer 5.0.x已停止维护，建议迁移至仍受支持的操作系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.cert.org/vendor_bulletins/VB-96.10.sco","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1965"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1428.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0763","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0763.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0509","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9109,\"outputTokens\":22,\"totalTokens\":10795}}","description":"WWW 站点的 cgi-bin 目录下错误地部署了 Perl、sh、csh 等脚本解释器程序，而非普通 CGI 脚本。远程攻击者可通过 HTTP 请求直接访问并执行这些解释器，向其传递特制参数从而在目标 Web 服务器上执行任意命令。该漏洞影响所有将 shell 解释器置于 Web 可访问 cgi-bin 目录的站点，攻击条件仅为攻击者能向目标站点发起 HTTP 请求，无需身份认证，可导致服务器被完全控制、数据泄露或沦为跳板，危害等级极严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0509"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1996-05-29T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:32.780","remediation":"立即从 Web 服务器 cgi-bin 目录中删除或移走 perl、sh、csh 等 shell 解释器脚本（如 perl、test-cgi 等），禁止将任何解释器置于可执行 CGI 路径下；在 Apache 等服务器配置中关闭不必要的 CGI 执行权限（如注释 ScriptAlias 或设置 Options -ExecCGI），并将 CGI 程序严格限制在受信任目录并仅保留必要的编译后二进制；同时升级 Web 服务器到已修复该默认配置的安全版本（如 Apache 1.3.27+/IIS 4.0 SP6a+），并以低权限专用账户运行 web 服务以减小危害。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/146","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/1999/CVE-1999-0509.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2f8583cd0e244c401900c481a78c07fe5535c09f/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0509.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0509","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1e2d061a60b9c6823d20cc72e51f709fadad54d2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0509.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0509.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/808b57c97f3c3a63ccc1ba2e5715700b4df9d9e8/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-fr45-fgh4-2qmm/GHSA-fr45-fgh4-2qmm.json","https://github.com/briandfoy/cpan-security-advisory/blob/228de67a7a4b13d017ca4a324923e49c94625191/IGNORE_CVEs","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/S/shells.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83213/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0763.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0779","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0779.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0522","title":"Sun NIS+ 系统关键表权限配置不当漏洞","description":"NIS+（网络信息服务增强版）中系统关键表（如 passwd）的权限设置不当，可能导致未授权用户读取或修改该表中的敏感账户信息。NIS+ 服务常用于 UNIX 环境下的集中用户管理，若 passwd 表权限配置过于宽松，远程攻击者可利用该缺陷获取系统账户哈希值，进而通过离线破解获取明文密码，或直接修改账户信息实现未授权访问。该漏洞影响早期 Solaris 等使用 NIS+ 服务的 UNIX 系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。修复措施包括严格限制 NIS+ 表的访问权限并遵循最小权限原则进行配置。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0522"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1996-05-28T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:34.470","remediation":"应限制 NIS+ 表（passwd, hosts, cred 等）权限为仅 root 可读写，使用 nischmod 命令将表权限设为 644 或更严格，通过 nisgrpadm 控制域访问范围。启用 NIS+ 的 DES 认证及 secure_rpc 防止未授权读取。如已停止维护，建议迁移至 LDAP + Kerberos 作为长期目录服务方案。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0522"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0779.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0066","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0066.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0019","title":"Data General DG/UX rpc.statd 文件创建或删除漏洞","description":"DG/UX 操作系统中 rpc.statd（NFS 状态监控守护进程）存在输入验证缺陷，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标系统发送特制的恶意请求，利用无效数据触发文件创建或删除操作。该漏洞可导致系统关键文件被篡改或删除，影响系统的正常服务运行和数据完整性，受影响的 DG/UX 版本范围广泛，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0019"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1996-04-24T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:21.823","remediation":"DG/UX 系统已停止支持无官方补丁，建议立即停止 rpc.statd 服务（`/etc/init.d/nfs.server stop`）并禁用 rpcbind 端口映射；在网络边界防火墙阻断 111(TCP/UDP) 端口对该主机的访问；如业务需要 NFS 功能，限制可访问来源 IP 并在 hosts.allow/deny 中仅允许受信主机连接 rpc.statd。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/135"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0066.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0191","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0191.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0078","title":"SCO OpenServer 和 UnixWare pcnfsd 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"pcnfsd（又称 rpc.pcnfsd）服务程序存在输入验证不当漏洞，本地攻击者可通过在 RPC 调用参数中注入恶意参数，进而修改目标系统文件权限或执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 SCO OpenServer 和 UnixWare 等操作系统版本，攻击者需拥有本地访问权限，CVSS 评分 1.9，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":1.9,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0078"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1996-04-18T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:31.737","remediation":"建议升级 SCO OpenServer 5.0.4 及以上版本或 UnixWare 2.0.1 及以上版本，其中已修复 pcnfsd 参数校验缺陷。若当前系统无法升级，可在 inetd 配置中注释 rpc.pcnfsd 行并重启 inetd 服务以禁用该 RPC 服务作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0078"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0191.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1333","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1333.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1103","title":"DEC OSF/1 dxconsole 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows 远程桌面授权服务远程代码执行漏洞","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1103"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1996-04-03T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:43.707","remediation":"升级 DEC OSF/1 至 3.2C 以上版本，或安装 DEC 官方安全补丁集。如无法升级，可移除 dxconsole 的 setuid 位或限制可执行权限，仅授权可信用户使用。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/g-18.shtml","http://www.cert.org/vendor_bulletins/VB-96.05.dec","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7138.php","http://www.tao.ca/fire/bos/0209.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/94380d498cb52b65d051c9bd443b6f2aa85bf8ec/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1103.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1103","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1103.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/cdbbe57bd34c799f670485304ef54912650bf03b/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1103.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/799c403529fad0f67d5473eea397e9968232a5ec/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5p9p-6x4x-p4x4/GHSA-5p9p-6x4x-p4x4.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88488/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154500_154600.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1103.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--19d1784b-7f1b-4b4f-9e02-9e3dda811549.json","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--19d1784b-7f1b-4b4f-9e02-9e3dda811549.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1333.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0175","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0175.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0070","title":"Apache NCSA HTTPd test-cgi 目录遍历信息泄露漏洞","description":"Apache 0.8.x/1.0.x 及 NCSA HTTPd 1.x 中的 test-cgi 程序存在目录列表泄露漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证，通过向目标服务器发送特制的 HTTP 请求即可触发该脚本的目录遍历功能，获取服务器上任意目录的文件列表，进而导致敏感信息（如配置文件、脚本源码等）泄露。该漏洞影响早期版本的 Apache 和 NCSA HTTPd 服务器，利用方式简单，危害中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0070"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1996-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:30.563","remediation":"升级到 Apache 2.0 及以上版本（该问题在 Apache 1.3.x 已修复），或直接移除 test-cgi 脚本及所在目录的执行权限。同时禁用 Apache 中 Options 指令的 Indexes 参数，防止目录列表泄露。如无法升级，在 httpd.conf 中将 test-cgi 目录的访问控制设置为 Deny from all。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://lists.apache.org/thread.html/rc5d27fc1e76dc5650e1a3f1db1de403120f4c2d041cb7352850455c2%40%3Cusers.httpd.apache.org%3E","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20435","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0070.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0070.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0070","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0070.json","https://github.com/CVEProject/cve-reference-ingest-data/blob/c8b30957414aefbd6ba0b766db0d40593ba36fba/references/CVE-1999-0070-2023-09-21-1730","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0070.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0070.md","https://github.com/decal/werdlists/blob/81edb463f7f6311c85defefaf75ac9cd58e5cfb9/exploit-info/symantec-attack-signatures.txt","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-93fg-xppj-x2xf/GHSA-93fg-xppj-x2xf.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/acunetix/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0070.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0175.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0175.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0291","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0291.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0141","title":"Oracle Java Bytecode Verifier 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Java Bytecode Verifier（字节码验证器）存在安全验证缺陷，恶意 Java Applet 可绕过沙箱限制，在用户浏览器中执行任意系统命令。攻击者通过构造特制的恶意 Applet 并嵌入网页，诱使用户使用 Netscape Navigator 等浏览器访问即可触发漏洞。该漏洞影响已安装 Java 运行环境的系统，CVSS 评分 3.7，危害等级低。建议用户禁用浏览器中的 Java Applet 支持或升级到修复版本。","severity":"LOW","score":3.7,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0141"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1996-03-29T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:41.103","remediation":"升级至 Sun Security Bulletin #134 对应修补版本（JDK 1.1.6 及以上），或安装 Netscape Navigator 安全更新。在现代系统上，由于所有主流浏览器已移除 Java Applet 支持，卸载旧版 JRE（如 Java 6/7/8）并在浏览器中彻底禁用 Java 插件作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/134"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0291.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0167","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0167.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0067","title":"NCSA HTTPd phf CGI 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"NCSA HTTPd 服务器自带的 phf CGI 程序存在操作系统命令注入漏洞（CWE-78）。远程攻击者无需身份认证，即可通过向 phf 发送包含 shell 元字符（如分号、管道符等）的特制 HTTP 请求，在服务器端以 Web 进程权限执行任意系统命令。该漏洞可导致完全控制目标服务器，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0067"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1996-03-20T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:30.077","remediation":"立即停止使用 NCSA httpd，升级至 Apache httpd 或 Nginx 等现代 Web 服务器，并删除或禁用 cgi-bin/phf 脚本。临时缓解措施：在 Web 服务器配置中限制 CGI 目录访问权限，对用户输入过滤 shell 元字符（;、`、|、$ 等），防止恶意字符传递至 CGI 程序。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-1996-06.html","http://www.osvdb.org/136","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/629"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0167.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0292","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0292.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0142","title":"Netscape Navigator Java Applet 安全限制绕过漏洞","description":"Netscape Navigator 2.0 及 Java Developer's Kit 1.0 中 Java Applet Security Manager 实现存在安全漏洞，未能正确限制小程序的网络连接权限，导致恶意 Java Applet 可突破安全沙箱限制，与任意远程主机建立网络连接，从而可能绕过同源策略窃取敏感信息或发起进一步攻击。攻击者只需诱导用户访问嵌有恶意小程序的网页即可触发，利用方式简单。该漏洞影响早期 Java 小程序的安全隔离机制，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0142"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1996-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:41.223","remediation":"升级至 Netscape Navigator 2.01 及以上版本或更新 Java 运行时环境，从根本上消除 Java 安全管理器绕过漏洞。亦可完全禁用浏览器中 Java Applet 执行权限，或更换为现代浏览器以彻底规避此类风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0142"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0292.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0418","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0418.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0233","title":"Microsoft IIS 1.0 .cmd/.bat 文件远程命令执行漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 1.0、Netscape Server 1.0/1.12 及 O'Reilly WebSite Professional 1.1b 等早期 Web 服务器在处理 .cmd 和 .bat 文件请求时存在远程命令执行漏洞。远程攻击者通过向受影响服务器发送包含 .cmd 或 .bat 后缀的 HTTP 请求，可导致服务器直接执行任意系统命令。该漏洞影响多种主流 Web 服务器软件，危害严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0233"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1996-02-25T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:58.010","remediation":"对于 Microsoft IIS 1.0，打开 Internet 服务管理器，删除 .bat 和 .cmd 扩展名的脚本映射，或升级至 IIS 2.0 及以上版本（已于后续版本中默认移除该映射）。对于 Netscape Server 1.0/1.12，升级至 Netscape Enterprise Server 2.0 或更高版本。对于 O'Reilly WebSite Professional 1.1b，升级至 WebSite Professional 2.0 或更高版本。鉴于以上产品均已终止支持且停止更新，强烈建议迁移至仍在安全维护周期内的现代 Web 服务器产品。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ148188","http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ155056","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20445","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0233.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0233","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0233.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0233.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-2752-8gwx-98x4/GHSA-2752-8gwx-98x4.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/web-iis.rules","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/invicti/vulnerabilities/db/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0233.yaml","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0233.json","https://github.com/magicsword-io/Magic-SigExplorer/blob/2c28b91b003429a144a687199ee99ebd26f1a343/Magic-SigExplorer/docs/cve_report.md","https://github.com/slacker247/GPDA/blob/fa9006d0877a691f1ddffe88799c844a3e8a669a/Aries/Sodi/Run/IDSrules/rule.989"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0418.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0418.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0418.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0293","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0293.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0143","title":"MIT Kerberos 4 密钥服务器会话密钥伪造漏洞","description":"Kerberos 4 密钥服务器存在会话密钥破解漏洞，攻击者可通过破解并伪造会话密钥来伪装成任意合法用户身份。该漏洞影响 Kerberos 4 密钥分发中心（KDC），攻击者无需高级权限即可实施身份欺骗攻击，可能导致未授权访问受保护网络资源。CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0143"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1996-02-21T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:41.347","remediation":"升级至 Kerberos 5 协议（MIT Kerberos 1.11+ 或 Active Directory 均已废弃 Kerberos 4），Kerberos 5 使用更强的加密算法和安全的会话密钥协商机制。如在旧系统中仍启用 Kerberos 4 兼容模式，应关闭 krb4 支持（设置 KRB5_KRB4_COMPAT=no），并禁用 Telnet/FTP 等明文传输通道以减少凭据泄露风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0143"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0293.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0236","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0236.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0103","title":"多厂商 UDP Echo/Chargen 服务数据包风暴拒绝服务漏洞","description":"UDP炸弹或UDP数据包风暴漏洞（UDP bomb/UDP packet storm）是指攻击者利用 UDP echo（回显）和 chargen（字符生成）等服务的组合特性，向目标服务器发送伪造源地址的数据包，使服务之间形成无限循环的数据包风暴，从而导致目标系统网络带宽耗尽、服务不可用。该漏洞影响早期 UNIX/Linux 系统中默认启用的 UDP 服务，属于拒绝服务类漏洞。攻击者无需认证即可远程发起攻击，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。该漏洞自 1999 年被发现至今仍可在未正确配置 UDP 服务的系统中利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0103"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1996-02-08T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:35.610","remediation":"禁用不必要的 UDP 服务（如 echo、chargen、time 等），在 /etc/inetd.conf 或 systemd socket 配置中注释或删除对应行并重启服务。在边界防火墙/路由器上阻止外部对 UDP 端口 7 (echo)、19 (chargen) 的访问，并限制内部 UDP 广播流量以防止放大攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://ics-cert.us-cert.gov/advisories/ICSMA-18-233-01","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/80171"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0236.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1285","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1285.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1491","title":"RedHat Linux 2.1 abuse.console 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"RedHat Linux 2.1 中的 abuse.console 程序在查找和执行 undrv 程序时使用相对路径名，导致本地用户可通过构造指向恶意程序的路径（如特洛伊木马程序），诱导 abuse.console 执行任意命令，从而实现本地权限提升。该漏洞影响 RedHat Linux 2.1 系统，攻击者需具备本地账户权限，通过控制 PATH 环境变量或创建同名恶意程序诱导 abuse.console 执行，从而提升至 root 权限。CVSS 评分 7.2，属于高危本地提权漏洞。Red Hat 已发布补丁修复该漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1491"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1996-02-02T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:33.307","remediation":"建议立即升级至 Red Hat Linux 2.1 修补版本（应用 Red Hat 发布的 errata 补丁 RHSA-1999:047-01），或升级至更新版本的 Red Hat Linux。若无法立即升级，可通过修复 /usr/sbin/abuse.console 中的相对路径调用问题（将 undrv 替换为绝对路径 /usr/sbin/undrv），并限制普通用户对 abuse.console 的执行权限（chmod 750 /usr/sbin/abuse.console）作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602167418994&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/354","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19279","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/df06113bb625f86b49f1950d55874a29f8e76a55/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1491.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1491","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1491.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/5297adfba5e91ee22e711c26c523b292d427c0d0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1491.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/90b464bbc2d1b64270a5771429f96b67fbe9e79b/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-33qc-p77x-82rf/GHSA-33qc-p77x-82rf.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1491.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154500_154600.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/354/info.html","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--fa7703be-a94b-4bb7-ad05-d57d42680df8.json","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--fa7703be-a94b-4bb7-ad05-d57d42680df8.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1285.toml"}]